quran[11{c,v,t}:
10,43,aur baaz aisay hain ke tumhari taraf dekhte hain. tokiya tum andhon ko rasta dikhao ge agarchay kuch bhi dekhte ( bhaltay ) nah hon
10,44,khuda to logon par kuch zulm nahi karta lekin log hi apne aap par zulm karte hain
10,45,aur jis din khuda un ko jama kere ga ( to woh duniya ki nisbat aisa khayaal karen ge ke ) goya ( wahan ) gharri bhar din se ziyada rahay hi nahi they ( aur ) aapas mein aik dosray ko shanakht bhi karen ge. jin logon ne khuda ke rubaroo haazir honay ko jhatlaya woh khasaray mein par gay aur raah yab nah hue
10,46,aur agar hum koi azaab jis ka un logon se wada karte hain tumhari aankhon ke samnay ( nazil ) karen ya ( is waqt jab ) tumhari muddat hayaat poori kar dein to un ko hamaray hi paas lout kar aana hai phir jo kuch yeh kar rahay hain khuda is ko dekh raha hai
10,47,aur har aik aُmt ki taraf se paighambar bheja gaya. jab un ka paighambar aata hai to unn mein insaaf ke sath faisla kar diya jata hai aur un par kuch zulm nahikiya jata
10,48,aur yeh kehte hain ke agar tum sachey ho to ( jis azaab ka ) yeh wada ( hai woh aeye ga ) kab ?
10,49,keh do ke mein apne nuqsaan aur faiday ka bhi kuch ikhtiyar nahi rakhta. magar jo khuda chahay. har aik ummat ke liye ( mout ka ) aik waqt muqarrar hai. jab woh waqt ajata hai to aik gharri bhi der nahi kar saktay aur nah jaldi kar saktay hain
10,50,keh do ke bhala dekho to agar is ka azaab tum par ( nagahan ) aajay raat ko ya din ko to phir gunehgaar kis baat ki jaldi karen ge
10,51,kiya jab woh aa waqay hoga tab is par imaan lao ge ( is waqt kaha jaye ga ke ) aur ab ( imaan laaye? ) is ke liye to tum jaldi machaya karte they
10,52,phir zalim logon se kaha jaye ga ke azaab daimi ka maza chako. ( ab ) tum inhen ( aamaal ) ka badla pao ge jo ( duniya mein ) karte rahay
10,53,aur tum se daryaft karte hain ke aaya yeh sach hai. keh do haan khuda ki qasam sach hai aur tum ( bhaag kar khuda ko ) aajiz nahi krsko ge
